1. "*Mama* mi je rekla da je zdrava." (My mom told me she was healthy.)
2. "Čini se da je *mama* zaboravila da me zove." (It looks like mom forgot to call me.)
3. "*Mamu* sam posetio prošlog vikenda." (I visited mom last weekend.)
4. "*Mami* sam rekao da ću se vratiti kući u večernjim satima." (I told mom I will be back home in the evening.)
5. "*Mamu* smo pozvali na večeru kod nas." (We invited mom for dinner at our house.)